    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >田野中的人是一个古老的仪式，它会奖励玩家财富和安全。在仪式过程中，玩家家中所有可以打开的门和物品都会被打开。玩家必须在午夜之前关闭所有的东西，以防田野中的人进入。即使最小的盒子没有关闭，它也能进入并带走你需要的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使者：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在这个仪式中，你可能会也可能不会在你的房子里遇到一个阴暗的人。他不是田野里的人，他是一个传令官。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051180/extras/d2aa4aabbaa6695a5a9a269cb69e7bad.poster.avif?t=1730059226\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051180/extras/d2aa4aabbaa6695a5a9a269cb69e7bad.webm?t=1730059226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051180/extras/d2aa4aabbaa6695a5a9a269cb69e7bad.mp4?t=1730059226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >但请牢记这个警告：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>不要看向田野！</strong> 如果你这样做了，你会看到一个四肢细长的男人开始向你的房子移动。你必须把自己锁在一个有十字架的安全房间里，然后它才能找到进去的路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051180/extras/d2bdadf6d98e6c2626ec4451755ddc71.poster.avif?t=1730059226\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051180/extras/d2bdadf6d98e6c2626ec4451755ddc71.webm?t=1730059226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051180/extras/d2bdadf6d98e6c2626ec4451755ddc71.mp4?t=1730059226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>独特地点：</strong> 该游戏有 6 个地点，每次玩时都不同。不要在同一个地方寻找物品。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051180/extras/61b09d6d12534037309edb8f723a8dac.poster.avif?t=1730059226\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051180/extras/61b09d6d12534037309edb8f723a8dac.webm?t=1730059226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051180/extras/61b09d6d12534037309edb8f723a8dac.mp4?t=1730059226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多重结局：</strong> 这种仪式可以以许多不同的方式结束，其中一些比其他方式更不幸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战：</strong> 与时间赛跑，同时可能避开哭泣者，使这种仪式变得困难。获得奖励是具有挑战性的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略：</strong> 找到使用设备和安全室的最佳方式。</p>",
